<a class="title" href="/nodes/97184/comments/1426142">Re: Android == Desktop (WTF?)</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/flagos" rel="author">flagos</a> (<a href="http://blog.lilibio.com/">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-24T11:13:18+01:00"><span class="date">le 24/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 11:13</span></time>.
Évalué à&nbsp;<span class="score">
3
</span>.
